    "body": "> df.drop([3:])\r\n\r\npandas can't do anything about the syntax error :) You can't do `__getitem__` on the parenthesis.\r\n\r\n> Perhaps it could be implementing by checking if labels do not exist then making df.drop([3:]) a wrapper for df.drop(np.arange(3,len(df)))?\r\n\r\nWe've been moving away from trying to guess the users intention. It's caused more trouble and confusion that convenience."
